{"tid":1475211,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[區議會戰線]九龍城啟德巴絲快入!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-08-15T11:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T20:29:38.000Z","uid":204163,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"185af17cfda91cb9c80cdcf4592a368762ee22c6","tid":1475211,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6S9x9Df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6S9x9Df.jpg&h=7e970d83&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n目前成個九龍城區重有兩個白區，就係啟德北同啟德東<br />\n住得係啟晴同德朗既，都知呢兩條邨有幾on9<br />\n但係唔係因為咁就放棄啊!<br />\n如果要放棄，咁呢兩個月以黎既努力同付出又為咩?<br />\n每一個可能都唔可以放棄<br />\n尤其經民聯呢d垃圾政黨，繼續蠶食會席<br />\n梁婉婷同何華漢自動當選，你甘心咩?<br />\n<br />\n我明依家開始可能太遲<br />\n但只要有心，永遠唔會太遲!<br />\n每個人的力量都好重要，啟晴同德朗的巴絲，和理非定勇武都好<br />\n區議會一戰，我地一定要贏!!!<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力!<br />\n<br />\ntg: <a href=\"http://t.me/kaitakselection\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkaitakselection&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=13c75c20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/kaitakselection</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎入黎討論，時間已經無多，我地要盡快行動!!!!"},{"pid":"fbe04d2dc51ca09a3452c4cfa41fc0b4cf53b748","tid":1475211,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:45:39.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39910f5b732d71bb34e60934c89a43838146c1d","tid":1475211,"uid":146975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e55b9cd0ca46791e224642cf20c5cfe516d4edf7","tid":1475211,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:53:45.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n最後都無人選<br />\n可以試下搵D100桑普<br />\n<br />\n佢之前話左<br />\n最後都仍然有選區無泛民競爭<br />\n佢可能會去選"},{"pid":"4f089c072efa8f2bbd2acc473a260e7553a206c6","tid":1475211,"uid":204163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:45:05.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid